        "content_html": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">VIP票权益：</span></strong><br>方天雷1v1签名合影会；<br>演出现场前区观演席位；<br>巡演官方限定纪念票根；<br>获得1次巡演盲盒抽取机会（概率掉落珍藏版限量专辑）</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0309/19/00/c5daf6d3ff944c109021fd260d6365df_768_5302_2484649.0x0.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"4418\"><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0309/19/00/16748a6bd74a40fda5dc2987c1de5467_768_3672_2169625.0x0.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"3060\"><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0309/19/00/b3dc308e8e3a47baa12aa53c771a0dde_768_3593_2046894.0x0.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"2994\"><img src=\"https://s2.showstart.com/img/2026/0309/19/00/9a67b773210f457d89302d956612d9bd_768_1627_1128208.0x0.jpg?imageMogr2/thumbnail/640x/gravity/Center/crop/640x\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"1356\"></p>"
